.\u201d I said, \u201cEven if he commits adultery\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13531,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/11\/hudud-hand-not-cut-petty-theft\/","url_meta":{"origin":6663,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hudud: Hand is not cut for petty theft, stealing food","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Rafi\u2019 ibn Khadeej reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not cut the hand of one who steals fruit, or steals from palm trees.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1449 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u00a0Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u062e\u064e\u062f\u0650\u064a\u062c\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11958,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/31\/wives-permission-husbands-sawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":6663,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Wives need permission from husband to voluntarily fast","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 31, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The 